{"tid":902429,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【忠義兩難存】迪士尼樂園內撐侵侵連任 狂迷一世被禁足","createTime":"2018-11-14T20:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T01:23:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a93a5cc4a35551b7024e816f941aef0ebdfd42","tid":902429,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T20:55:46.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普的一名狂熱支持者，本月在佛羅里達州迪士尼樂園的「飛濺山」（Splash Mountain），大玩激流活動時，由於展示標語支持特朗普連任，結果被指違反樂園守則，並被拍下照片，更逐出園區。<br />\n涉事的特朗普粉絲Dion Cini，經常在美國各地展示支持特朗普的橫額，把照片上傳到Facebook。其帳戶內一張11月10日上傳的照片顯示，他在佛羅里達州迪士尼樂園內激流泛舟時，再次展示「Trump 2020」標語，結果被驅逐出園區，沒收一年通行證之餘，更被禁以後不得再進入渡假村範圍，包括樂園、酒店及「Disney Springs」購物區。<br />\nCini並非首次被迪士尼驅趕，今年9月，他在同一個樂園內的小鎮大街（Main Street）火車站，「快閃」展示巨形橫額，寫上「請投票讓特朗普2020年連任，保持美國偉大」（Re-elect Donald J. Trump, Keep America great! 2020）的字句。當時，園方一度沒收其通行證，但Cini保證不會再犯後，才獲園方歸還通行證。<br />\n霍士新聞指，除了是特朗普狂迷，Dion Cini也是迪士尼粉絲，連續購買全年通行證長達26年。<br />\n全球的迪士尼樂園都有明文規定，任何人未經授權，不得在園區內進行任何活動、示威、演說、煽動其他遊客，或展示旗幟、橫額或招牌，作商業用途。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181115/large/1542212483_5808.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181115%2Flarge%2F1542212483_5808.jpg&h=ea1f5f96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181115/58914190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181115%2F58914190&d=sIGfopfUIAdzml7A%2BFiBPpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=00b612b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181115%2F58914190&h=c1035009\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181115/58914190</a>"},{"pid":"631e8db5df0c13b8aee97c9676498e7894b64521","tid":902429,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T22:55:50.000Z","msg":"迪士尼呢d去一次就夠啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條友買足26年年票係咪痴線架"},{"pid":"f734c1a9e6c3e43000b29db63df0219c7b6a2fdf","tid":902429,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T23:07:52.000Z","msg":"應該係義不容情"},{"pid":"95996630c00601764425ce7946ff1156ca50545b","tid":902429,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T23:29:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e52fea7bef592c92774cf08948387705f8a6312c","tid":902429,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T00:01:02.000Z","msg":"犯咩事<br />\n有作商業用途？"},{"pid":"16b230dc6160e170f34d38a39c3eb29a682edbb7","tid":902429,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T00:29:48.000Z","msg":"試下舉支持民主黨贏眾議院先嘛 唔識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0dd916ba7c7ba14f9a74cdb2e74af0091c2c9d7","tid":902429,"uid":121580,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e52fea7bef592c92774cf08948387705f8a6312c","tid":902429,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T00:01:02.000Z","msg":"犯咩事<br />\n有作商業用途？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:15:53.000Z","msg":"政治宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果個個都好似佢咁個公園就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f56139a9d975a021d468328e5cd8429038477a5","tid":902429,"uid":95520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:20:37.000Z","msg":"原本想屌鳩迪士尼<br />\n但你真係一早明文寫定咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f661b166b649d6d299d1058ffde2f3c6dc45fd","tid":902429,"uid":693,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0f56139a9d975a021d468328e5cd8429038477a5","tid":902429,"uid":95520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:20:37.000Z","msg":"原本想屌鳩迪士尼<br />\n但你真係一早明文寫定咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:23:33.000Z","msg